            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段回吐，上證綜指以4076點開市，跌10點或0.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14925點，亦跌70點或0.47%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌13點或0.29%，開報4757點；創業板指數開市報3623點，跌25點或0.69%。</p>\n</div>",
