            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指跌111點報25814點 寧德時代配股後低開6.74%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段偏軟，恒生指數開市報25814點，跌111點或0.43%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4623點，跌16點或0.33%；國企指數以8711點開市，跌44點或0.51%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多家公司相繼配股或換股債集資，其中傳聞多時的寧德時代(03750)配股集資50億美元終於落實，配股價較該股昨收市價折讓7%；該股今早應聲低開6.74%，在競價時段以630元開市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國宏橋(01378)則擬發102億元人民幣的1年期零息換股債，該股今早開報33.76元，跌3.65%。至於其他公布配股的公司中，361度(01361)今早開報6.7元，跌3.18%；達力普(01921)則開報6.02元，升0.33%；博泰車聯(02889)開報141元，跌0.35%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-web_CATL-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股繼續互有升跌，阿里巴巴(09988)擬分拆嘉興園區於深圳以基礎設施REIT方式上市，已獲港交所(00388)批准；該股今早開報128.8元，跌1.08%。騰訊(00700)開報476元，跌0.54%；滙控(00005)開報139.6元，跌0.43%；友邦(01299)開報83.8元，升0.72%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，今日有兩隻新股掛牌，曦智科技(01879)以880元開市，較招股價183.2元高3.8倍；邁威生物(02493)以28.3元開市，較招股價27.64元高2.39%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15930469-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c111%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125814%e9%bb%9e-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 09:28:11",
