            "title": "兆威電機首季淨利跌逾25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兆威電機(02692)首季歸屬於上市公司股東的淨利潤4095.1萬元(人民幣‧下同)，按年跌25.15%。基本每股數益0.17元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">扣除非經常性損益淨利潤3213.91萬元，按年跌31.89%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">營業收入3.57億元，按年跌2.74%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15930433-%e5%85%86%e5%a8%81%e9%9b%bb%e6%a9%9f%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be25",
